<h2 class="bold font-l">Stevonnie</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Steven, a Human-Gem hybrid, accidentally fuses with the human Connie and they become Stevonnie. Their fusion then becomes a visible sign of their growing romantic interests for each other as the series progresses. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
